<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Pacote cadastrado</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background: #f4f4f4; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 40px auto; background: #fff; border-radius: 8px; overflow: hidden; box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,.1); }
    .header { background: #1a1a2e; padding: 32px; text-align: center; }
    .header h1 { color: #fff; margin: 0; font-size: 24px; }
    .body { padding: 32px; color: #333; }
    .body p { line-height: 1.6; }
    .details { background: #f9f9f9; border-radius: 6px; padding: 16px 24px; margin: 24px 0; }
    .details table { width: 100%; border-collapse: collapse; }
    .details td { padding: 8px 0; font-size: 14px; }
    .details td:first-child { color: #666; width: 40%; }
    .details td:last-child { font-weight: bold; }
    .footer { text-align: center; padding: 24px; font-size: 12px; color: #aaa; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Pacote cadastrado com sucesso!</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="body">
      <p>Olá, <strong>{{firstName}} {{lastName}}</strong>!</p>
      <p>O seu pacote foi registado no nosso sistema. Consulte os detalhes abaixo:</p>

      <div class="details">
        <table>
          <tr>
            <td>Estado</td>
            <td>{{status}}</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>Morada</td>
            <td>{{address.street}}, {{address.number}}{{#if address.complement}} — {{address.complement}}{{/if}}</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>Cidade</td>
            <td>{{address.city}} — {{address.countryDivision}}</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td>Código Postal</td>
            <td>{{address.zipCode}}</td>
          </tr>
          {{#if collectDay}}
          <tr>
            <td>Dia de recolha</td>
            <td>{{collectDay}}</td>
          </tr>
          {{/if}}
          {{#if collectTime}}
          <tr>
            <td>Hora de recolha</td>
            <td>{{collectTime}}</td>
          </tr>
          {{/if}}
        </table>
      </div>

      <p>Em caso de dúvidas, entre em contacto com a nossa equipa.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>© {{year}} Retex. Todos os direitos reservados.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
